commit message: minor fix of number of components
Support for loading /data/local/init.mac when starting up

automatic semi-colon addition
support of maxima manual in en, ja and de. De is in en folder.

Session menu is added to support ssave(), srestore(), and playback()
from menu.
Settings menu is added to allow choosing manual language.

csetup() uses text output extensively, which has not been dealt well.
This improves the treatment of text output generally. As a consequence,
the csetup() works fine now.
csetup() text output is now properly handled.

New feature: RBT = reuse by touch technology. Displayed input
expressions are now touchable objects. When they are touched, they
appear in the input area for reuse.
Manual language selection is now stored in the preference.

Code clean up, Copyright 2013 added, itensor example now properly
displayed.
